tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE RobotExperiments (
    experiment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    robot_name VARCHAR(100),
    experiment_description TEXT,
    start_time TIMESTAMPTZ,
    end_time TIMESTAMPTZ
);

CREATE TABLE test_data (
    test_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    test_name VARCHAR(100),
    experiment_id INT,
    test_data JSONB,
    FOREIGN KEY (experiment_id) REFERENCES simulation_results(simulation_id)
);

CREATE TABLE robot_tests (
    test_id INT,
    robot_id INT,
    test_result JSONB,
    FOREIGN KEY (test_id) REFERENCES test_data(test_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (robot_id) REFERENCES virtual_robots(robot_id)
);

CREATE TABLE experiment_logs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    simulation_id INT,
    log_description TEXT,
    log_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (simulation_id) REFERENCES simulation_results(simulation_id)
);
